CPANPLUS provides a programming interface and command-line access to
the Comprehensive Perl Archive Network (CPAN).  CPANPLUS can download
and install Perl distributions for you.

Please type "perldoc CPANPLUS" after installation to see the module
usage information.  For shell usage, please consult "perldoc cpanp".

perl-CPANPLUS-Dist-Slackware, which creates Slackware compatible
packages from Perl distributions, is an optional dependency.
